# getcontractstate Method

Queries contract information, according to the contract script hash. 

## Parameter Description

Script_hashï¼šContract script hash 

## Example

Request body:

```json
{
  "jsonrpc": "2.0",
  "method": "getcontractstate",
  "params": ["dc675afc61a7c0f7b3d2682bf6e1d8ed865a0e5f"],
  "id": 1
}
```

Response body:

```json
{
    "jsonrpc": "2.0",
    "id": 1,
    "result": {
        "version": 0,
        "hash": "0xdc675afc61a7c0f7b3d2682bf6e1d8ed865a0e5f",
        "script": "",
        "parameters": [
            "ByteArray"
        ],
        "returntype": "ByteArray",
        "name": "Woolong",
        "code_version": "0.9.2",
        "author": "lllwvlvwlll",
        "email": "lllwvlvwlll@gmail.com",
        "description": "GO NEO!!!",
        "properties": {
            "storage": true,
            "dynamic_invoke": false
        }
    }
}
```
